game.name: Elsa Restaurant Steak Taco Salad
game.description:
Elsa  Restaurant Steak Taco Salad is an awesome free online cooking game especially for girls from different age groups. You will get a chance to become a chef in Elsa restaurant in this brand new kitchen game. Today her cute sister, Anna has decided to visit her restaurant and, for that reason, you will have to prepare a special late for her. In order to create the best steak taco salad, it is good for you to follow the recipe of the family. 

Start this cool html5 game with preparing the chopped vegetables. In the next step, fry and cut the meat and then get ready to prepare the desired food items. Your abilities of the chef will be challenged while exploring all the tasks of this excellent girl cooking game. As you know that Elsa has invested a lot of money in her restaurant, so please do your best to prepare steak taco salad. Chop scallions, garlic, onions and red peppers perfectly. Also, chop the steak with a knife.

Use a pan, pour some oil in it and heat it up on the stove to a required temperature. Add meat to it and fry it for some time. Check and put the vegetables at the right time. You also have to spice everything with pepper and salt and stir properly. To get a perfect shape, you are also required to put some tortillas into the taco holder. Fill up your lovely tortillas with this mixture. Your scrumptious and colourful dish is ready to serve now.
